snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed.client import AsyncSeedMultiUrlEnvironment

client = AsyncSeedMultiUrlEnvironment(
    token="YOUR_TOKEN",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.ec_2.boot_instance(
        size="string",
    )


asyncio.run(
    main(),
)
